  "events": [
    {
      "event_id": "02009026_e00001",
      "play_id": "02009026",
      "scene_id": "02009026_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 1,
      "seq_in_scene": 1,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "林冲上。",
      "text_length": 4
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02009026_e00002",
      "play_id": "02009026",
      "scene_id": "02009026_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 2,
      "seq_in_scene": 2,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "仙吕宫调点绛唇",
      "speakers": [
        "林冲"
      ],
      "text": "数尽更筹，听残银漏，逃秦寇，好教俺，有国难投，那答儿相求救。",
      "text_length": 30
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02009026_e00003",
      "play_id": "02009026",
      "scene_id": "02009026_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 3,
      "seq_in_scene": 3,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "recitation",
      "mode_label": "念",
      "speakers": [
        "林冲"
      ],
      "text": "欲送登高千里目，愁云低锁衡阳路。鱼书不至雁无凭，今番空作悲风赋。回首西山日影斜，天涯孤客真难渡。丈夫有泪不轻弹，只因未到伤心处。",
      "text_length": 64
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02009026_e00004",
      "play_id": "02009026",
      "scene_id": "02009026_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 4,
      "seq_in_scene": 4,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "林冲"
      ],
      "text": "俺，林冲。一时愤怒，持剑杀死高俅奸细二人。官府严拿甚紧，多蒙柴大官人，与俺书信一封，荐往梁山。日间不敢走路，只得黑夜而行。呀，适才间星明月朗，一霎时月暗云迷。山路崎岖，叫俺怎生行走。呀，前面黑洞洞的，想是人家村庄，待俺趱上看来。呀，我当是村庄人家，原来是座古庙。门儿半掩半开，待我矮身而进。黑夜之间，辨不出是何神圣。神圣呵，神圣。保佑弟子林冲哦。呵呀。",
      "text_length": 176
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02009026_e00005",
      "play_id": "02009026",
      "scene_id": "02009026_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 5,
      "seq_in_scene": 5,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "林冲看。",
      "text_length": 4
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02009026_e00006",
      "play_id": "02009026",
      "scene_id": "02009026_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 6,
      "seq_in_scene": 6,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "林冲"
      ],
      "text": "幸喜四顾无人，待我将门关闭上。",
      "text_length": 15
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02009026_e00007",
      "play_id": "02009026",
      "scene_id": "02009026_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 7,
      "seq_in_scene": 7,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "林冲拜。",
      "text_length": 4
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02009026_e00008",
      "play_id": "02009026",
      "scene_id": "02009026_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 8,
      "seq_in_scene": 8,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "林冲"
      ],
      "text": "神圣呵神圣，保佑弟子林冲，早到梁山，借得兵来，清了君侧，报了深仇，定当重修庙宇，再塑金身。",
      "text_length": 45
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02009026_e00009",
      "play_id": "02009026",
      "scene_id": "02009026_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 9,
      "seq_in_scene": 9,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "林冲困。",
      "text_length": 4
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02009026_e00010",
      "play_id": "02009026",
      "scene_id": "02009026_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 10,
      "seq_in_scene": 10,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "林冲"
      ],
      "text": "哎哈，身体困倦，就在神圣案前，打一盹睡，起来再走。正是：",
      "text_length": 28
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02009026_e00011",
      "play_id": "02009026",
      "scene_id": "02009026_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 11,
      "seq_in_scene": 11,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "recitation",
      "mode_label": "念",
      "speakers": [
        "林冲"
      ],
      "text": "一觉放开心定稳，梦魂千里到阳台。",
      "text_length": 16
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02009026_e00012",
      "play_id": "02009026",
      "scene_id": "02009026_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 12,
      "seq_in_scene": 12,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "内白",
      "speakers": [
        "神圣"
      ],
      "text": "林冲醒来，休得睡梦。我乃迦蓝神圣，警告于你：后有金枪手徐宁，带领官兵五百，追至黄河渡口，拿你甚紧。此刻不走，等待何时。",
      "text_length": 59
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02009026_e00013",
      "play_id": "02009026",
      "scene_id": "02009026_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 13,
      "seq_in_scene": 13,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "林冲"
      ],
      "text": "是，弟子就行，弟子就行。呀，适才神圣言道：后有金枪手徐宁，带领官兵五百名，追至黄河渡口，拿我甚紧。此时不走，等待何时。拜过神圣，开了庙门，甩开大步，直奔梁山走遭也。",
      "text_length": 82
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02009026_e00014",
      "play_id": "02009026",
      "scene_id": "02009026_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 14,
      "seq_in_scene": 14,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "双调新水令",
      "speakers": [
        "林冲"
      ],
      "text": "按龙泉血泪洒征袍，恨天涯一身流落。专心投水浒，回首望天朝。急急走，忙忙逃，顾不得忠和孝。",
      "text_length": 44
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02009026_e00015",
      "play_id": "02009026",
      "scene_id": "02009026_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 15,
      "seq_in_scene": 15,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "驻马听",
      "speakers": [
        "林冲"
      ],
      "text": "良夜迢迢，良夜迢迢，投宿休将门户敲。遥瞻残月，暗度重关，我急急走荒郊。身轻不惮路途遥，心忙又恐人惊觉。吓得俺魄散魂销，红尘中，误了俺，五陵年少。",
      "text_length": 72
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02009026_e00016",
      "play_id": "02009026",
      "scene_id": "02009026_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 16,
      "seq_in_scene": 16,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "林冲"
      ],
      "text": "想俺林冲，在那八十万军中，作一个禁军教头。征那吐蕃的时节呵。",
      "text_length": 30
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02009026_e00017",
      "play_id": "02009026",
      "scene_id": "02009026_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 17,
      "seq_in_scene": 17,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "折桂令",
      "speakers": [
        "林冲"
      ],
      "text": "俺指望封侯万里班超，生比做叛国红巾，做了背主黄巢。却便似脱韝苍鹰，离笼狡兔，拆网腾蛟，救国难谁诛正卯。掌刑法难得皋陶，只这鬓发萧萧，行李萧条。博得个斗转天回，",
      "text_length": 79
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02009026_e00018",
      "play_id": "02009026",
      "scene_id": "02009026_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 18,
      "seq_in_scene": 18,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "夹白",
      "speakers": [
        "林冲"
      ],
      "text": "高俅呵，高俅！",
      "text_length": 7
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02009026_e00019",
      "play_id": "02009026",
      "scene_id": "02009026_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 19,
      "seq_in_scene": 19,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "折桂令",
      "speakers": [
        "林冲"
      ],
      "text": "管教你海沸山摇。",
      "text_length": 8
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02009026_e00020",
      "play_id": "02009026",
      "scene_id": "02009026_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 20,
      "seq_in_scene": 20,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "雁儿落带得胜令",
      "speakers": [
        "林冲"
      ],
      "text": "望家乡，去路遥，想母妻，将谁靠。俺这里吉凶未可知，他那里生死应难料。呀，吓得俺，汗津津，身上似汤浇，急煎煎，心内似火烧。幼妻室，今何在，老萱堂，空丧了。劬劳父母的恩难报，悲号，叹英雄气怎消，英雄的气怎消！",
      "text_length": 102
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02009026_e00021",
      "play_id": "02009026",
      "scene_id": "02009026_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 21,
      "seq_in_scene": 21,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "沽美酒带太平令",
      "speakers": [
        "林冲"
      ],
      "text": "怀揣着雪刃刀，怀揣着雪刃刀，行一步哭号啕，急走羊肠去路遥。",
      "text_length": 29
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02009026_e00022",
      "play_id": "02009026",
      "scene_id": "02009026_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 22,
      "seq_in_scene": 22,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "夹白",
      "speakers": [
        "林冲"
      ],
      "text": "老天哪！",
      "text_length": 4
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02009026_e00023",
      "play_id": "02009026",
      "scene_id": "02009026_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 23,
      "seq_in_scene": 23,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "沽美酒带太平令",
      "speakers": [
        "林冲"
      ],
      "text": "怎能够明星下照，昏惨惨云迷雾罩。疏喇喇风吹叶落，听山林声声虎啸。绕溪涧哀哀猿叫，俺呵，吓得我魂飘胆销。心惊路遥，呀，百忙里走不出山前古道。",
      "text_length": 69
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02009026_e00024",
      "play_id": "02009026",
      "scene_id": "02009026_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 24,
      "seq_in_scene": 24,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "收江南",
      "speakers": [
        "林冲"
      ],
      "text": "呀，又只见乌鸦阵阵起松梢，听数声残角断渔樵。忙投村店伴寂寥，想亲帏梦杳，想亲帏梦杳，空随风雨度良宵。",
      "text_length": 50
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02009026_e00025",
      "play_id": "02009026",
      "scene_id": "02009026_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 25,
      "seq_in_scene": 25,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "煞尾",
      "speakers": [
        "林冲"
      ],
      "text": "一宵儿奔走荒郊，穷性命挣得一条。到梁山请得兵来，",
      "text_length": 24
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02009026_e00026",
      "play_id": "02009026",
      "scene_id": "02009026_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 26,
      "seq_in_scene": 26,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "夹白",
      "speakers": [
        "林冲"
      ],
      "text": "高俅吓，高俅！",
      "text_length": 7
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02009026_e00027",
      "play_id": "02009026",
      "scene_id": "02009026_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 27,
      "seq_in_scene": 27,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "煞尾",
      "speakers": [
        "林冲"
      ],
      "text": "誓把你奸臣扫！",
      "text_length": 7
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02009026_e00028",
      "play_id": "02009026",
      "scene_id": "02009026_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 28,
      "seq_in_scene": 28,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "林冲"
      ],
      "text": "呀，前面已是梁山，甩开大步走走也。",
      "text_length": 17
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02009026_e00029",
      "play_id": "02009026",
      "scene_id": "02009026_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 29,
      "seq_in_scene": 29,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "林冲下。",
      "text_length": 4
    }
  ],
